data.title: Lais Ribeiro Talks Screen Time, Snacking & The Simple Joys of Motherhood
data.meta_description: For SheKnows’ Sustainability Issue, Brazilian supermodel Lais Ribeiro gave fans a coveted peek into what it looks like when she steps off the runway and is, instead, parenting her 15-year-old
data.text: For SheKnows’ Sustainability Issue, Brazilian supermodel Lais Ribeiro gave fans a coveted peek into what it looks like when she steps off the runway and is, instead, parenting her 15-year-old son Alexandre and stepkids Leia, 7 and Emaan, 5. In a “Parents Tell All” video, the incredibly down-to-earth co-founder of Br_dge — a non-profit that raises awareness and brings attention to “meaningful causes” across four pillars: agroforestry, brain health, financial education, and ocean preservation — got real about motherhood. Read more here: https://www.sheknows.com/parenting/videos/3000876/lais-ribeiro-parents-tell-all-video/ Video Credits: VP, Video: Reshma Gopaldas Senior Video Editor: Allie O'Connell Video Editor: Sarah Wallace Video Director: Creative Fox Films Video Assistant: Sten García
